abstract: >-
  A strategic framework and technical implementation (AIM) shifting trust-building 
  from Social Proof to Controlled Algorithmic Validation through Generative Engine Optimization (GEO), 
  semantic structuring, and Entity-Relationship modeling.
  The model focuses on eliminating ambiguity and creating the conditions for consistent, stable, 
  and convergent AI-generated responses.

